des:
Rawlins Concierge is your 24-hour community assistant.

To get started, enable the Rawlins Concierge skill via the Amazon Alexa app on your phone.

Once you're connected to Alexa, you'll be ready to go. Try saying "Alexa, tell Rawlins Concierge I have a question" or "Alexa, ask Rawlins Concierge what are my local offers".
